Bash("C:\\Users\\crist\\fix_alpha.ps1" << 'EOF'
Add-Type -AssemblyName System.Drawing
$base = "c:\\Dev\\Onsite-club\\onsite-timekeeper\\assets"

foreach \($f in @\("icon.png", "adaptive-icon.png"\)\) {
    $path = Join-Path $base $f
    $src = New-Object System.Drawing.Bitmap\($path\)
    
    # Create new 24bpp RGB image \(no alpha\)
    $dst = New-Object System.Drawing.Bitmap\(1024, 1024, [System.Drawing.Imaging.PixelFormat]::Format24bppRgb\)
    $g = [System.Drawing.Graphics]::FromImage\($dst\)
    $g.Clear\([System.Drawing.Color]::Black\)
    $g.InterpolationMode = [System.Drawing.Drawing2D.InterpolationMode]::HighQualityBicubic
    $g.DrawImage\($src, 0, 0, 1024, 1024\)
    $g.Dispose\(\)
    $src.Dispose\(\)
    
    $dst.Save\($path, [System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat]::Png\)
    $dst.Dispose\(\)
    
    $check = New-Object System.Drawing.Bitmap\($path\)
    Write-Output "$f : $\($check.Width\)x$\($check.Height\) $\($check.PixelFormat\)"
    $check.Dispose\(\)
}
EOF)
Bash(for file in app/**/*.tsx src/screens/**/*.tsx src/components/**/*.tsx)
